  status = 'active',
  namecom_order_id = '26487104',
  cloudflare_zone_id = (SELECT result FROM JSON_TABLE(
    (SELECT JSON_EXTRACT(
      (SELECT CAST(SUBSTRING_INDEX(SUBSTRING_INDEX(
        (SELECT GROUP_CONCAT(result) FROM (
          SELECT JSON_EXTRACT(response, '$.result[0].id') as result
          FROM (
            SELECT '{"result":[{"id":"448dd94143105c68ee22ee8dce995278"}]}' as response
          ) t
        ) t2),
        '"', 2), '"', -1) AS CHAR)), '$.result[0].id'
    )),
    '$' COLUMNS (id VARCHAR(255) PATH '$')
  ) jt LIMIT 1)),
  nameservers = JSON_ARRAY('annabel.ns.cloudflare.com', 'braden.ns.cloudflare.com'),
  dns_status = 'configured',
  ssl_status = 'pending',
  updated_at = NOW()
WHERE domain_name = 'lulubaby.xyz';
